            <div class="text-6xl text-white">🦋</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Wildlife Conservation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Protecting endangered species and their habitats through dedicated conservation efforts.
            </p>
